name: All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Bonnie Doon - Bonnie Doon Morning - Lines 2022/01/16
description:
All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Bonnie Doon - Bonnie Doon Morning - Lines 2022/01/16
The "All the Hidden Quanta - Postcard from ..." series using Processing visual arts language, explores the concept that we are surrounded by the unseen (unacknowledged? unrealised?), constantly in flux world of quanta. This project was processed from real time camera captures during the morning of Sunday January 16, 2022. If you look closely you may spot the traces of boats at play on the lake. mp4, 1280x960px, 25fps, 50seconds(please loop), 64.4MB.
